CocoaPods Environment Setup

Using the default Ruby install will require you to use sudo when installing gems.

$ sudo gem install cocoapods

---------------------------------------------------

Project Setup

1. Do not open the project with Xcode
2. Open the terminal
	$ cd [project directory]
	$ pod install

From now on, open xxx.xcworkspace instead of xxx.xcodeproj.

